vote.title: A resolution authorizing (1) an extension to the Credit Agreement with JPMorgan Chase Bank, National Association in support of the City of Dallas, Texas General Obligation Commercial Paper Notes Series A, and Series B; and (2) the execution of agreements pertaining thereto and resolving other matters related thereto for a one-year extension from November 28, 2025 to November 27, 2026 - Not to exceed $1,855,000 - Financing: Debt Service Fund
